{"tid":1635203,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗又拉左個小朋友","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:47:03.000Z","uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51f347035df4789bdb2ea3d78b24399b59b49ce6","tid":1635203,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxhvBca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxhvBca.png&h=7d318698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggvANiX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggvANiX.png&h=98724f8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97f212a7938175d28113347446a66f24c0fb501d","tid":1635203,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"【facebook戰線】大家一齊report曬D垃圾page，等佢地重蹈點新聞嘅覆轍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eewfbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eewfbS</a><br />\n<br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejgzzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejgzzS</a>"},{"pid":"435ca4f7a959ddff1d1d8fa586553edaaccca5a1","tid":1635203,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"84e50ef41d43390453039bebde9c95aeccc839a7","tid":1635203,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"39a258b080e8d5c02ab17c8066e8c5fcbaf47307","tid":1635203,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef48d783ad6cfd9f386f7a4187ac20785ec81b3d","tid":1635203,"uid":320306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"推 認人"},{"pid":"109223ceb67df1fc8c080647f7f2fc56c96074ef","tid":1635203,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}